comments: Bazley (OKC) legally contests Ingram's (NOP) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Graham (NOP) is moving alongside Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and marginal contact occurs prior to Gilgeous-Alexander's gather.
Jones (NOP) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession should have been awarded to Oklahoma City.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) steps slightly forward towards Hart (NOP) and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Favors (OKC) is already in Hart's (NOP) path and is firming up when he absorbs the contact.
Valanciunas (NOP) briefly grasps Favors' (OKC) arm during rebounding and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
Valanciunas (NOP) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Oklahoma City.
Valanciunas (NOP) briefly grasps Favors' (OKC) arm and marginal contact occurs as Valanciunas secures the rebound.
Valanciunas (NOP) is already in Williams' (OKC) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the contact.
Favors (OKC) is moving alongside Graham's (NOP) path and the marginal contact during the driving shot attempt is caused by Graham.
Favors (OKC) makes contact with the ball below rim height and does not affect Graham's (NOP) shot attempt's ability to be scored.
Bazley (OKC) brushes Ingram's (NOP) hand and marginal contact occurs as Ingram reaches to secure the ball.
Jones (NOP) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Wiggins (OKC) commits a take foul on Ingram (NOP).

Temple (NOP) brings his hand forward to commit a take foul on GIlgeous-Alexander (OKC), and contact occurs to Gilgeous-Alexander's left arm.  Additionally, the contact occurs prior to Gilgeous-Alexander's gather and upward shooting motion.
